import React from "react"; import Card from "react-bootstrap/Card"; import { ImPointRight } from "react-icons/im"; function AboutCard() { return (

Hi Everyone, I am Yutika Kiran Vora from Arizona, USA
I am currently employed as a software developer at Privoro LLC.
I am pursuing my Master of Science in Information Technology (Project Management) from Arizona State University, Arizona, USA.

Apart from coding, some other activities that I love to do!

  • Dancing
  • Playing Badminton
  • Travelling
); } export default AboutCard;
